    "name": "vLLM OpenAI-Compatible Server",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "description": {
      "content": "vLLM is a high-throughput open-source inference and serving engine for\nLLMs. Running `vllm serve` exposes an OpenAI-compatible REST API plus\nvLLM-specific endpoints. Authentication is via a server-startup\n`--api-key` flag; clients supply it as a Bearer token in the\nAuthorization header (matching the OpenAI Python client).\n\n\nContact Support:\n Name: vLLM Documentation",
      "type": "text/plain"
    }
  }
